Diablo stepped rather daintily over roots and branches in the forest, 
using his four hooves to ther full agility. One could never do with 
tripping up and embaressing themselves. His stalk eyes looked in the 
direction of every sound he heard, and his scythe like blade on the 
end of his tail was held high behind him.

His emerald green eyes held a glint of arrogance in them as he 
surveyed the woods. Diablo looked forward to meeting the Alliance 
leader.. and finding out whether he or she was a total idiot or one 
actually worthy of leading. He chuckled silently to himself. Having 
no mouth allowed him to think using the mind, but since he had met no 
other bots he had never tested it out.

A branch that was directly in his path was snapped in two with his 
tail, and the bot never slowed his pace. His internal scanners told 
him there was a base somewhere near here.. but which one, he couldn't 
be sure..
